yesterday sucked like oh my god keep in mind: this happened at 7 pm broad daylight with people around so...... me, elizabeth, jonathan, and peter hung out at the gym till it closed we called jesse and met him at the hat place cuz jonathans stuff was in his trunk after food we gnabbed yoshi at eudemonia he had to take his bike home and devin/jack needed a ride we decided to meet up at ohlone park that was a very very bad idea the 6 of us get to ohlone park and are just fucking around jesse wanders a way for a minute [to the water fountain or something of that nature] and is followed back by two black dudes they try to start shit with jesse and yoshi it doesnt work we decide to leave and meet at the cemetary jesse and yoshi cross the street to go to his car they are still being harassed the rest of us follow a bit behind because we had to get peters shoe out of the tree as soon as we get to the sidewalk on the other side of the street we see one guy grab yoshis head phones yoshi starts screaming he gets socked in the face and goes down straight onto his forehead jesse gets punched a second later and also goes down but not as hard the dudes run some of the neighbors come out and call the police yoshi doesnt know where he is and cant remember what happened the police come the fire department come the paramedics come the crime scene unit comes they catch the dudes a few blocks away they are dumb and went home one apparently is well known by the berkeley police yoshi is taken by ambulance to the hospital the other 5 of us give police reports 3 of us are taken to i.d. the guys they take us back and eventually let us leave jonathan and elizabeth get picked up by parents peter gets a ride home from a cop i take jesse to the e.r. because hes bleeding from a gash next to his eye we wait for 5.5 hours before he is admitted it takes 2 hours for them to get around to fixing him yoshi left the hospital around 1.30 am we waited for jesse till 4 they are both fine sore but fine my saturday night sucked to say the least -end-
